00:18:46.062 --> 00:18:47.862
Itu semakin mendekat.

321
00:18:47.862 --> 00:18:49.562
Dia tidak lari.

322
00:19:02.062 --> 00:19:03.562
Kalian tetap di belakang!

323
00:19:09.362 --> 00:19:11.262
